OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,FA 7-year-old boy is on course to raise
OL,7,F#100,000 in memory of his dad who died
OL,8,Ffollowing a heart transplant at the
OL,9,FFreeman Hospital in Newcastle in May
OL,10,F2018.
OL,12,FGeorge Hughes from Wigan was just 18
OL,13,Fmonths old when his dad Dave had a
OL,14,Fheart transplant. Sadly complications
OL,15,Fled to Dave passing away eleven weeks
OL,16,Flater.
