OL,6,FDuring those eleven weeks the Hughes
OL,7,Ffamily were supported by the Freeman
OL,8,FHeart and Lung Transplant Association
OL,9,Fwhich helped them with accommodation,
OL,10,Ftravel and emotional support.
OL,12,FGeorge's mum Louise Hughes who married
OL,13,FDave at the Freeman Hospital started
OL,14,Ffundraising with George in 2019.
