OL,6,FIt was the little things like they
OL,7,Fwould call and say let me pay your
OL,8,Fpetrol because we were back and forth
OL,9,Ffrom Newcastle to Wigan and that was a
OL,10,Flot of money. You could ask them for
OL,11,Fanything you want and it wasn't just
OL,12,Fabout the money either, the people who
OL,13,Frun it are all transplant patients and
OL,14,Ffamilies so they know the situation."
