OL,6,F"We are keeping Dave's memory alive.
OL,7,FGeorge and the family talk a lot about
OL,8,Ftransplants and organ donation is key.
OL,9,FPeople should talk about organ
OL,10,Fdonation, share your wishes, talk
OL,11,Fabout it with your family, you can
OL,12,Fsave so many lives and be a super hero
OL,13,Feven when you pass away."
OL,15,FAs well as fundraising Louise Hughes
OL,16,Fwas so inspired by the nurses who
OL,17,Fcared for Dave that the year after he
OL,18,Fdied she started training to become a
OL,19,Fnurse.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
